	<element name="Keyblade Warrior" type="Class" source="KH" id="ID_KH_CLASS_KEYBLADE_WARRIOR">
		<description>
		<p> The Keyblade Warrior is trained in the use of the Keyblade to drive back the forces of Darkness.</p>
		<h3>Class Features</h3>
		<p>As a Keyblade Warrior you gain the following class features.</p>
		<h5 class="caption">HIT POINTS</h5>
			<ul class="unstyled">
				<li><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d8 per Keyblade Warrior level</li>
				<li><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 8 + your Constitution modifier</li>
				<li><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d8 (or 6) + your Constitution modifier per Keyblade Warrior level after 1st</li>
			</ul>
		<h5 class="caption">PROFICIENCIES</h5>
			<ul class="unstyled mb">
				<li><strong>Armor:</strong> Medium Armor</li>
				<li><strong>Weapons:</strong> Martial Weapons</li>
				<li><strong>Tools:</strong> None</li>
			</ul>
			<ul class="unstyled">
				<li><strong>Saving Throws:</strong>Constitution</li>
			</ul>
			<h5 class="caption">EQUIPMENT</h5>
			<p>You start with the following equipment, in addition to the equipment granted by your background:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Keyblade</li>
				<li>a Chain Shirt</li>
				<li>Two sets of tools or instruments.</li>
				<li>10 gp</li>
			</ul>
